Class MockRequest

java.lang.Object

      org.jogger.test.MockRequest
All Implemented Interfaces:
Request
public class MockRequest
extends AbstractRequest

This is a Request implementation that stores the request state in attributes. Useful for testing Jogger without a Servlet Container.

Author:
German Escobar
